{"tid":1814662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本話人”帶風向”都係捉鬼既一種","createTime":"2020-01-07T04:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:13:52.000Z","uid":182197,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0286952ea63b189cf6c8eb3bc425ac359137b8a","tid":1814662,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"試代入下，你係14年，16年，經歷無數既割席篤灰<br />\n19年，你諗住終於全民覺醒，食幾多子彈tg都無怨無悔<br />\n但點知轉個頭俾人捉鬼，搞到要著草<br />\n咁樣俾自己人背叛，發下晦氣都唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點係，就算d退場post係五毛出諗住打擊我哋士氣<br />\n我相信d post都某程度上反映左前線既不滿，怨氣</span><br />\n我地作為和理非，係應該好好反省思考，而唔係回句帶風向就當無事發生<br />\n用五毛標籤去無視手足既心情，同捉鬼根本無分別<br />\n<br />\n大家認清事實啦，就算我係和理非，都feel到前線愈來愈少人<br />\n原因除左被拉既之外，我相信一定有d係因為部分不思進取既和理非造成<br />\n我希望2020 1月1係最後一單捉鬼<br />\n以後，捉鬼者鬼"},{"pid":"afb336382882e938557ea3bbdba3b6b1b9a7d531","tid":1814662,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6498390198910e96648c023d87a72dad91173e22","tid":1814662,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"見咁多小隊呢排都退出，趁住呢個機會我地都⋯⋯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814649</a>"},{"pid":"b0d7fef630de5198a00ae8561dfc960428409ac3","tid":1814662,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n連登仔<br />\n贏就靜靜雞<br />\n港獨又靜靜雞<br />\nQuit game 就大大聲<br />\n捉鬼又大大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb2dd2ad2eb6767a24183addb7cf047f47740e61","tid":1814662,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d7fef630de5198a00ae8561dfc960428409ac3","tid":1814662,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span sty